<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ol>
      <li><p>122. Sample response: </p><p>[@@@@@@@@] WARNING: Fix Image.</p><img alt="Subtraction." role="image" src="../../../../../../figures/tikz-file-148981.svg"/><p>[@@@@@@@@] WARNING: Fix Image.</p><img alt="Expand image" src="../../../../../assets/expand-9ef5655e2d1b5ba286de1390c97f4243f15e264c89106027f5d071073ab562bb.png" title="Expand image"/><p>[@@@@@@@@] WARNING: Fix Image.</p><img alt="Subtraction." role="image" src="../../../../../../figures/tikz-file-148981.svg" width="80%"/></li>
      <li>192. Sample response: I subtracted 200 from 382 to get 182. Then I added 10 back.</li>
      <li><p>639. Sample response: </p><p>[@@@@@@@@] WARNING: Fix Image.</p><img alt="Subtraction." role="image" src="../../../../../../figures/tikz-file-148982.svg"/><p>[@@@@@@@@] WARNING: Fix Image.</p><img alt="Expand image" src="../../../../../assets/expand-9ef5655e2d1b5ba286de1390c97f4243f15e264c89106027f5d071073ab562bb.png" title="Expand image"/><p>[@@@@@@@@] WARNING: Fix Image.</p><img alt="Subtraction." role="image" src="../../../../../../figures/tikz-file-148982.svg" width="80%"/></li>
      <li>122. Sample response: I knew that 2 more would get me to 480. 20 more is 500. 100 more is 600. I had to count up 122 to get to 600.</li>
      <li><p>88. Sample response: </p><p>[@@@@@@@@] WARNING: Fix Image.</p><img alt="Subtraction." role="image" src="../../../../../../figures/tikz-file-148983.svg"/><p>[@@@@@@@@] WARNING: Fix Image.</p><img alt="Expand image" src="../../../../../assets/expand-9ef5655e2d1b5ba286de1390c97f4243f15e264c89106027f5d071073ab562bb.png" title="Expand image"/><p>[@@@@@@@@] WARNING: Fix Image.</p><img alt="Subtraction." role="image" src="../../../../../../figures/tikz-file-148983.svg" width="80%"/></li>
